67
00:04:07,440 --> 00:04:08,880
prestasi Yutian.

68
00:04:09,759 --> 00:04:11,960
Jika hari ini ada orang
ingin mengakuisisi Yutian,

69
00:04:12,039 --> 00:04:13,080
