70
00:04:13,320 --> 00:04:14,520
Silakan kalian pikirkan dulu.

71
00:04:15,279 --> 00:04:16,600
Itu menunjukkan nilai Yutian.

72
00:04:16,760 --> 00:04:17,600
Benar.

73
00:04:17,760 --> 00:04:19,160
Ini menunjukkan nilai Yutian…

74
00:04:19,239 --> 00:04:20,440
dan potensi perkembangannya.

75
00:04:20,720 --> 00:04:21,799
Aku ingin bertanya kepada kalian.

76
00:04:22,359 --> 00:04:23,519
Siapa yang bersedia memasukkan uang…

77
00:04:23,519 --> 00:04:25,040
ke dalam lubang besar
yang tak punya harapan?

78
00:04:26,640 --> 00:04:27,440
Jadi,

79
00:04:27,559 --> 00:04:29,559
inilah alasan dasar Yutian diakuisisi.

80
00:04:30,040 --> 00:04:31,600
Terima kasih
atas perhatian kalian terhadap Yutian.

81
00:04:36,040 --> 00:04:36,799
Akuisisi?

82
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:38,119
Kenapa menerima akuisisi?

83
00:04:38,920 --> 00:04:40,359
Ayo… kita tanya.

84
00:04:40,799 --> 00:04:42,920
Direktur Jiang, maksudmu
ingin menerima akuisisi?

85
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:44,320
