126
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:33,839
Kak!

127
00:06:35,160 --> 00:06:36,480
Aku sudah melihat konferensi pers.

128
00:06:38,519 --> 00:06:39,559
Sangat keren.

129
00:06:40,679 --> 00:06:42,959
Kata-kata itu
sangat melampiaskan amarah.

130
